{"tid":325050,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鳩達:蟲洞計劃正式啟動","createTime":"2017-07-17T02:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T01:46:41.000Z","uid":33890,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f85766fbfd317c19033784f4f8d4c0dac5051bf","tid":325050,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"【蟲洞計劃】之一：突破次元限制，重建民意基礎<br />\n「補選」是政權安排給民主派的鬥獸場，只要拋出「議席」這個利餌，各黨自然鬥個你死我活，相互消耗。<br />\n且看單是有人拋出「總辭」建議，民主派的矛頭就馬上由政府轉向總辭倡議者，可謂效用顯著。<br />\n政權讓民主派掉進議席之鬥獸鐵籠之中，一來可消減反政府壓力，二來通過民主派相互撕殺的醜態，進一步削減民主派的道德感召力。<br />\n其實，自從佔領運動篤灰不斷、立法會選舉亂潑污水、掌心雷動計劃尤如出千、宣誓事件兒戲胡鬧、特首選舉支持建制鬍鬚，這一連串事件，已將民主派的道德高地壓到地平線以下。<br />\n將會出現的「補選」，則有如黑洞，會將香港民主運動僅剩的光環，吸乾吸淨，拉住無盡虛無之中。<br />\n眼下運動最大的困境，莫過於民眾已經徹底失去信任，不願再相信任何政黨及政治人物，香港政壇已徹底失去道德力量，難以感召大眾。<br />\n要突破困局，不單要有衝出重圍的力量，該能量可要巨大到足以突破次元。<br />\n運用「蟲洞計劃」，我們要以突破次元的思維，再次將散失於時間洪流中的道德力量找回來！<br />\n既然民主派拒絕「總辭」，面對「補選」，唯一能夠贏回港人信心的方法，就是所有政黨及所有政治人物、議政人士，全部都不要參選！<br />\n因為民眾已經徹底厭惡政壇，所有舊有的政治人物出現，都會勾起他們的厭惡。<br />\n如果真要參選「補選」，就要有全新的代理人，要為了這個「補選」成立一個全新的「系統」！<br />\n這「補選系統」，建立就純粹為了議席，由「系統」找出六個完全沒有任何政治經歷的人物，由他們作代理參選，而所有民主派動員一切力量團結一致全力支持。<br />\n完全沒有政治經歷的人，足以勝任議事工作嗎？不！當選後他們不是負責議事，他們只是代理，他們在議會一切投票及發言，皆會由「系統」提供的平台，由大眾公議決定，代理人只是代理。<br />\n六個全無政治經歷的代理人，當選後甚至要交出全部薪酬及津貼，交由「系統」的平台，讓大眾公議所有款項的使用方法。<br />\n這樣子，就完全沒有任何「議席利益」了！<br />\n通過這個「蟲洞」，民主派就能把民意力量，穿越時空阻隔，重新贏回來！<br />\n當然，這只是理想狀況，實質操作還有技術問題：誰人設置管理「系統」？如何不讓政黨干預介入？否則又會變回另一個黨啊。如何選出沒有政治經歷的代理人？由誰負責的「系統」去選？<br />\n這些都是需要解決的問題，我當然也有草案，同樣是超越次元的構想，但先按下不表，下回分解～～"},{"pid":"07ef4a84ea256c0127f04c5c82079e35db4f7dc2","tid":325050,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd9db071d6da574cca88b28658a7d3bdeb412cb4","tid":325050,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"發言係即時互動，無政治經歷嘅人點答到爹？<br />\n點可以確保修改完議案後喺投票前，透過系統表決？<br />\n個決定又點樣先有高認受性？最後必然會變成個別政黨嘅傀儡。"},{"pid":"5febba8bff081f7dc8a6dffb1217968a0b4f016a","tid":325050,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"課金啦！"},{"pid":"c04b1da746a83f22728567db5124721b8b7ee783","tid":325050,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 講出黎唔笑<br />\n叫鄭生做第1個囉<br />\n想人比黎夾住? <br />\nbtw 反正攪咩都係選唔到架啦"},{"pid":"aed373a79c0ec7ba06ccd00cba70db61ecb2dc88","tid":325050,"uid":93074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:52:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce082971982950ea059233d187ce7ca9580f4951","tid":325050,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發言係即時互動，無政治經歷嘅人點答到爹？<br />\n點可以確保修改完議案後喺投票前，透過系統表決？<br />\n個決定又點樣先有高認受性？最後必然會變成個別政黨嘅傀儡。</blockquote><br />\n所以香港搞乜都唔成"},{"pid":"3903e17cfbaf6b4200dd9f5ef361366a5609ce09","tid":325050,"uid":37081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>發言係即時互動，無政治經歷嘅人點答到爹？<br />\n點可以確保修改完議案後喺投票前，透過系統表決？<br />\n個決定又點樣先有高認受性？最後必然會變成個別政黨嘅傀儡。</blockquote><br />\n所以香港搞乜都唔成</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係依家各黨派之間失去哂互相 又或者係各懷鬼胎<br />\n無論邊個出黎參選都會俾人指責係鬼<br />\n就好似青政同胡國興咁<br />\n代理人呢個身份好難係黨派間有公信力<br />\n而且選民都冇人會信<br />\n最重要係熱狗誠信已經破產"},{"pid":"00b90d45bd4b4fd9c46771fd5111068bfef5d7ad","tid":325050,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:38:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"369b08978679f0106dc5a3e9b1208bcbeb9e1756","tid":325050,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>發言係即時互動，無政治經歷嘅人點答到爹？<br />\n點可以確保修改完議案後喺投票前，透過系統表決？<br />\n個決定又點樣先有高認受性？最後必然會變成個別政黨嘅傀儡。</blockquote><br />\n所以香港搞乜都唔成</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有就係依家各黨派之間失去哂互相 又或者係各懷鬼胎<br />\n無論邊個出黎參選都會俾人指責係鬼<br />\n就好似青政同胡國興咁<br />\n代理人呢個身份好難係黨派間有公信力<br />\n而且選民都冇人會信<br />\n最重要係熱狗誠信已經破產</blockquote><br />\n熱狗凍貓都無用"},{"pid":"eff51c7618c4d9441e34e6f6e1b5052047514368","tid":325050,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a23eb29750d1f5a5ab6a9ad5352718149babaf","tid":325050,"uid":127203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"出底牌了， 將自己掛牌出售， 搵政黨收留做橫子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d64f1266e2c403d28a4565712e0a889c822be1f","tid":325050,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"佢係咪想話熱狗做嗰幾個代理人<br />\n叫人推佢地入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb32403ce39a7430fead47b7705da74b8282121","tid":325050,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"當選後甚至要交出全部薪酬及津貼，交由「系統」的平台&lt;--------系統會收比幾多成行政費?"},{"pid":"5030e718430c3be10f29b0df729c738ff51ed59e","tid":325050,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:33:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcc755d156039ab945c2daff312128022faf6944","tid":325050,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:44:29.000Z","msg":"泛民新西保朱凱迪唔保旗主"},{"pid":"b767bf56914cc1b15fa182b5f6991783af642135","tid":325050,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當選後甚至要交出全部薪酬及津貼，交由「系統」的平台&lt;--------系統會收比幾多成行政費?</blockquote><br />\n建立平台 你唔信熱狗 你未參考雷動果陣時嘅經驗整個出嚟囉<br />\n熱狗都要保證自己唔再拆大台<br />\n同埋盤數點樣透明化 用起邊 用落去補貼6個被DQ嘅人又得唔得?<br />\n咁6個代理人薪酬又點計?"},{"pid":"03172fc1a84931d45db854dfd1ae963cac0f42fe","tid":325050,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當選後甚至要交出全部薪酬及津貼，交由「系統」的平台&lt;--------系統會收比幾多成行政費?</blockquote><br />\n建立平台 你唔信熱狗 你未參考雷動果陣時嘅經驗整個出嚟囉<br />\n熱狗都要保證自己唔再拆大台<br />\n同埋盤數點樣透明化 用起邊 用落去補貼6個被DQ嘅人又得唔得?<br />\n咁6個代理人薪酬又點計?</blockquote><br />\n先唔講9達又頄UP D咩<br />\n但大家嘅共識似乎係 今次要拎哂6個位一定要雷動 再加埋本土派唔好互相拉票<br />\n面子問題佢先唔講呢個前切<br />\n作為政治TRADE OFF又好點都好 佢起碼擺左自己個價起度"},{"pid":"18b58cf261f0f1d4c57680f80a9c19b209b2f891","tid":325050,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有痴線佬"},{"pid":"03d9433180ab1e20a5f1358dd9d114ca8a5faeef","tid":325050,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95d51c8be51f79f36dbdc3c77a6b16f0ff064a52","tid":325050,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"洗咩6個呀，搵呀蟲太一個咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蟲洞計山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac97e20d14be51eaf88578cd9a9065b7b8bf2e4","tid":325050,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗咩6個呀，搵呀蟲太一個咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蟲洞計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"eabe609451c3842337a6d3cd39d1ab20441cc971","tid":325050,"uid":62537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"又有新名目收課金"},{"pid":"8ae92fd5e5e3e99556c66fdbbac8ac20f6ddc69f","tid":325050,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"牙達又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班仆街記得準時課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n課金呀，屌你老母臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15959f8f4e2d1b3b51f67117ec39014d713bf62d","tid":325050,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"呢個計劃同共產主義一撚樣, 無視人性係自撚私"}]}